Trial.Scientific_title:
A Phase-II, Randomised, Double-blind, Parallel-group, Proof-of-concept Trial to Investigate ABBV-4083 given for 7 or 14 Days or in Combination with Albendazole in Subjects with Onchocerca volvulus Infection, comprising:
Part 1 to Investigate Safety, Tolerability, Efficacy for Dose-Ranging and Pharmacokinetics;
Part 2 to Investigate Efficacy of Selected Doses, Safety, Tolerability and Pharmacokinetics
